casebody.data:
BAYVIEW LOAN SERVICING, LLC, Appellant,
v.
Andrew Joseph GREENWELL a/k/a Andrew J. Greenwell, Appellee. Case No. 5D17-2340 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Fifth District. Opinion filed August 31, 2018 Melisa Manganelli, of the Law Offices of Mandel, Manganelli & Leider, P.A., Boca Raton, for Appellant. Richard J. Mockler, of Stay In My Home, P.A., St. Petersburg, and Latasha C. Scott, of Lord Scott, PLLC, Tampa, for Appellee. ON CONCESSION OF ERROR PER CURIAM.

Pursuant to Appellee's Concession of Error, we reverse the summary final judgment and remand this matter to the trial court for further proceedings.

REVERSED and REMANDED.

PALMER, ORFINGER, and WALLIS, JJ., concur.
